# 🔥 TRICK QUESTIONS (VERY IMPORTANT)

---

### ❓ Can we catch multiple exceptions in one catch?

```java
catch (IOException | SQLException e)
```

👉 Yes (Java 7+)

---

---

### ❓ Can we write code after throw?

👉 ❌ No (unreachable code)

---

---

### ❓ Can constructor throw exception?

👉 ✅ Yes

---

---

### ❓ Can finally have return?

👉 Yes (but not recommended)

---

---

### ❓ Which block executes first?

👉 try → catch → finally

---

---

# 🧪 SCENARIO QUESTIONS (INTERVIEW LEVEL)

---

### ❓ What happens here?

```java
try {
    return 1;
} finally {
    return 2;
}
```

👉 **Answer:** 2
👉 finally overrides return

---

---

### ❓ Output?

```java
